00:42:58,033 --> 00:42:59,660
[Masami in Japanese]

489
00:43:00,995 --> 00:43:02,538
[Kikuo in Japanese]

490
00:43:04,665 --> 00:43:06,333
-[Masami]
-[Kikuo]

491
00:43:08,252 --> 00:43:10,296
[Masami]

