00:43:28,647 --> 00:43:29,315
[Ogawa]

496
00:43:31,525 --> 00:43:33,068
[Ogawa]

497
00:43:33,110 --> 00:43:34,486
[Kikuo]

498
00:43:34,528 --> 00:43:35,904
[in English] Are you coming?

499
00:43:37,489 --> 00:43:38,532
Yeah.

