00:44:02,389 --> 00:44:04,016
[Phillip]

506
00:44:11,023 --> 00:44:12,650
[Kikuo]

507
00:44:12,691 --> 00:44:16,403
[in English]
Heaven on your tongue.

508
00:44:16,945 --> 00:44:19,114
[chuckles]

509
00:44:20,532 --> 00:44:22,284
[speaking Japanese]

510
00:44:25,663 --> 00:44:27,539
-[in English] You try.
-[Phillip chuckles]

511
00:44:32,294 --> 00:44:34,380
-[hisses]
-[chuckles]

