531
00:46:23,489 --> 00:46:25,407
Kikuo-san. Kikuo-san!

532
00:46:25,449 --> 00:46:26,617
Hey, hey! Stop, stop, stop!

533
00:46:26,658 --> 00:46:27,868
-Kikuo-san!
-[horn honks]

534
00:46:27,910 --> 00:46:29,036
Hey, where are you going?

535
00:46:29,077 --> 00:46:30,245
[in Japanese]

